`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Belgarion is one of the main Implementers of this MUD.	He is, for all intents
and purposes, Overlord of Prophecy.  Since he's dealing with the large matters
that affect the entire world, everyday problems should be resolved elsewhere. 

 Yes, he has the ability to strike fear into the other Immortals...but he's
just so darned cute that they can't help but to like him.

